      <pdf>utina2.pdf</pdf>
      <abstract>               
Discrete contol system with a  periodic nonlinearity is considered.  
Its important feature is  the number of cycle-slipping of the transient 
regime. In the paper by means of Lyapunov  direct method and  
Bakaev-Guzh technique for differentiable functions  
the estimation of the number of cycle--slipping  is established. 
Yakubovich--Kalman theorem is also used. 
Therefore the main theorem of the paper is formulated as 
a frequency-domain criterion. 
</abstract>
      <title>Multiparametric Friequency-Domain Criterion for the Estimation of the Number of Cycle--Slipping in Discrete Phase Systems. </title>
    </articleInfo>
